<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Crizaldo Cuesta - Professional Driver Resume</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        /* Custom styles for professional look and feel */
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8fa;
        }
        .section-title {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #047857; /* Dark green border */
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .card {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }
        .experience-item {
            border-left: 3px solid #d1d5db;
            padding-left: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .experience-bullet {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }
        .experience-bullet li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .experience-bullet li:before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #059669; /* Medium green bullet */
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        /* Styles specifically for printing (PDF generation) */
        @media print {
            body {
                background-color: white !important;
            }
            .card {
                box-shadow: none !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
                margin: 0 !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-4 sm:p-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 md:p-10 rounded-xl card">

        <!-- Header: Name and Title -->
        <header class="text-center pb-6 mb-6 border-b-2 border-gray-200">
            <h1 class="4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 tracking-tight">Crizaldo S. Cuesta</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mt-2">Professional Driver & Transportation Specialist</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl section-title">Contact Information</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-gray-700">
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> Peace Valley, Bulacao, Cebu City</p>
                <p><strong>Date of Birth:</strong> March 10, 1973</p>
                <!-- Mobile and Email removed per user request -->
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Objective -->
        <div class="mb-8 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
            <h2 class="text-xl section-title border-none mb-2">Objective</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">To secure a responsible and stable **Driver** position where I can utilize my **20 years of extensive experience** in operating 4-wheel vehicles and buses, along with my excellent knowledge of local routes and commitment to safety and timely delivery.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Skills and Qualifications -->
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl section-title">Key Skills & Qualifications</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-gray-700 experience-bullet">
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-700">Extensive Experience:</span> 20 years operating light and heavy-duty vehicles.</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-700">Vehicle Expertise:</span> Highly proficient in driving Buses and various 4-wheeled vehicles (cars, light trucks).</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-700">Route Knowledge:</span> Excellent familiarity with Cebu City and surrounding area routes.</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-700">Safety Record:</span> Strong commitment to adherence to all traffic laws and safety regulations.</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-700">Reliability:</span> Proven track record of punctuality and efficiency in completing schedules.</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-700">Maintenance:</span> Competent in pre-trip inspection and routine vehicle checks.</li>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Work Experience -->
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl section-title">Work Experience (20 Years Total)</h2>

            <div class="experience-item">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Bus Driver / Transportation Specialist</h3>
                <p class="text-md font-medium text-green-600">Various Employers / Long-Term Contract Driving</p>
                <p class="text-sm italic text-gray-500">Total Driving Experience: 20 Years</p>
                <ul class="mt-2 text-gray-700 experience-bullet">
                    <li>Safely operated and managed commercial **buses** for long-distance/commuter routes, prioritizing passenger safety and comfort.</li>
                    <li>Maintained strict adherence to demanding time schedules and route plans, demonstrating high reliability.</li>
                    <li>Conducted daily pre-and-post trip vehicle inspections to ensure all systems were operational and compliant with safety standards.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-item mt-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">4-Wheel Vehicle Driver (Logistics/Personnel)</h3>
                <p class="text-md font-medium text-green-600">Various Employers / Personal & Family Transport</p>
                <p class="text-sm italic text-gray-500">Total Driving Experience: 20 Years</p>
                <ul class="mt-2 text-gray-700 experience-bullet">
                    <li>Handled the safe and efficient operation of various **4-wheeled vehicles** for company logistics, delivery, and personnel transport.</li>
                    <li>Managed vehicle cleanliness and minor maintenance, minimizing downtime and ensuring vehicle readiness.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer Note -->
        <footer class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200 text-sm text-center text-gray-500">
            <p>References and detailed work history available upon request.</p>
        </footer>

    </div>

    <!-- Floating Print/PDF Button -->
    <button onclick="window.print()" class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full shadow-xl transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 print:hidden flex items-center space-x-2 z-50">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 4v3H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v3a2 2 0 002 2h1v2a2 2 0 002 2h6a2 2 0 002-2v-2h1a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V4a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2zm1 0h8v3H6V4zm.5 10a.5.5 0 000 1h6a.5.5 0 000-1h-6zm0-2a.5.5 0 000 1h6a.5.5 0 000-1h-6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <span>Download PDF</span>
    </button>
</body>
</html>
